---
const yearsExp = new Date().getFullYear() - 2012;
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="fade-in">
    <div class="section-label">
      <span class="section-label-line"></span>
      <span class="section-label-prefix">~/about</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">The person behind the code</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-content fade-in">
      <p>
        I'm a Full Stack Developer based in <strong>Cochin, Kerala</strong>, currently working at
        <strong>BEO Software Pvt. Ltd</strong>. With over {yearsExp} years in the industry, I've had the privilege of
        working across the entire software stack — from crafting pixel-perfect frontends to designing
        resilient backend architectures and building developer tooling.
      </p>
      <p>
        What drives me is the joy of solving real problems with well-crafted code. I don't believe in
        being locked into one language or framework. Whether it's <strong>TypeScript</strong> for a NestJS
        backend, <strong>Rust</strong> for a performant CLI, <strong>Go</strong> for container tooling, or
        <strong>Python</strong> for data processing — I pick the right tool for the job.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I'm not writing production code, I'm building open-source developer tools, experimenting with
        new technologies, or writing about what I've learned.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-highlights fade-in">
      <div class="highlight-card card">
        <div class="highlight-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6" /><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Polyglot Developer</h3>
          <p>Fluent in 8+ languages — choosing the best tool for each problem</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-card card">
        <div class="highlight-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5" /><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>CLI Craftsman</h3>
          <p>Obsessed with building tools that live in the terminal</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-card card">
        <div class="highlight-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" /><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" /><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Full Stack Thinker</h3>
          <p>From databases to dashboards, infrastructure to interfaces</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .about-content strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .highlight-card {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .highlight-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .highlight-card p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
